1. The site verifies if you have entered a proper usable email,by sending a verifying code to it,also it checks if your entry no. has proper parameters like branch code,or the year,or your email has keyword 'iitd' in it.
2.There is a forum where you can post possible doubts.You can add a functionality to search them(which I did not think of adding then).
3.Admin can block a user for a certain amount of time.
4.The users can send a complaint regarding a review,any content or adding new professors or courses.
5.You can search professors by their reaearch interests also.
6.You can search courses according to their descripyion or content.
7.Users's home page shows all his ratings and reviews.
8.Admin can send user a warning or appreciation for his work.
 
